Daily Coronavirus Cases in Australia Data

corona_aus.Rd

This dataset contains the daily case numbers and the total number of daily cases for 8 states/territories in Australia, namely, ACT, NSW, Victoria, WA, NT, SA and Queensland. It has 7 variables and around 6,220+ rows, which is updated on a continual basis.

corona_aus

Format

An object of class grouped_df (inherits from tbl_df, tbl, data.frame) with 6230 rows and 7 columns.

Source

Coronavirus Package

Details

The data is disaggregated using 7 keys:

Date:The date the case numbers are recorded on.
Type:The type of coronavirus case i.e. death, recovered or confirmed.
Province:The state or territory the case is from.
Lat:The latitude of the state/territory that has the case.
Long:The longitude of the state/territory that has the case.
Cases:The number of cases.
Cases_total:The total number of cases.
